A hidden leak can waste thousands of gallons and rot framing before you ever see a stain. We use acoustic and thermal tools to pinpoint the leak so we open up the smallest possible area to fix it.

## Signs you may have a hidden leak

- A water bill that crept up with no change in usage
- Warm spots on the floor or a constantly running meter
- Musty smells or paint that's bubbling

We find it, fix it, and document it for your insurer if you need that.
